<div type="commentary">
<p rend="stanza" n="5">Stanza 5 consists only of two <foreign>pāda</foreign>s. According to LR, the remaining <foreign>pāda</foreign>s can be supplied from CP 1 of 1913-14 (the unpublished Veḍatalūru grant), lines 7-8 on plate 2, as follows: <foreign>mr̥ṇmayan tu caturaṁga-balaṁ vā kṣipram eva vilayaṁ gatam ājau</foreign>.</p>
</div>



